Question: Techship Inc. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Techship Inc.

CES 2024

- Techship will be exhibiting at the Consumer Electronics Show (CES) in Las Vegas, showcasing advancements in 5G, Wi-Fi, antennas, and adapters. The event will take place from January 9–12, 2024, in the North Hall, booth #10971. Customers, suppliers, and friends are invited to schedule a meeting by emailing americas@techship.com.
